Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好暖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 振作啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能睡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是登山女生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我已經不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是你一個人活下去也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登頂成功 「女子力」升級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人去當大眾情人囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大眾情人~ 大眾情人~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好一起攀登回憶中的山峰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷 開著空調就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雪村葵 今年高一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直是室內派 但最近也開始對登山感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 冬天的富士山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 竟然丟下別人只顧自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你太絕情了 什麼大眾情人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做的夢 找我抱怨也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平時不攢人品 才會反映到我的夢裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你有理 算你有理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你還夢到回憶中的山峰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我 要架帳篷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算我的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我進入山友圈的就是這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住帳篷吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.97,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合目：登山進度 一般來說從山腳到山頂共分十合（也有一些山有十以上的合）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這帳篷能一下子住四個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看它疊起來很小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架起來很寬敞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快架起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人能架起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕鬆鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡按著 你把骨架穿進套管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,套管？骨架？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是套管 把骨架穿進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來再穿一根進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把骨架的兩頭穿進扣環
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣環是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡也穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加最後一把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的帳篷 架起來也不難嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說我為什麼在日向家院子裡架帳篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山裡露營？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約上可可娜醬和小楓學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去露營啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好！好主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 飯還沒好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和朋友約好去露營
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露營？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著吃的去野炊 再在帳篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友去露營？ 只有女孩子去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去日向家住一晚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 日向的爸爸也在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別給人家添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 我們就在日向家的院子裡露營了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 我們開始打樁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(785,640)}Peg
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打狗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是Pug 沙皮狗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Peg可是樁子、釘子的意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樁子就說樁子 裝什麼裝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,略微朝外側傾斜 要釘到底喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把繩索鉤在地樁上 固定住帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功告成！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 搭得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寬敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把手腳伸開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜醬！小楓學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們也是山友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是比我們高一年級的小楓學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光在學校是學姐 在登山方面也是我們的先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個 是中學生 可可娜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哇 好棒的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子力可高了 是個治癒系女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買晚餐的材料來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐這樣做過飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算做過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米淘好之後 先在水中浸一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天用的是碳烤爐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾的是火候掌控不到「先弱後強」的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「先弱後強」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古人形容做飯火候的俗語喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「孩子餓哭了也不能打開鍋蓋」！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋子被頂開的話就加上重物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到米湯不往外溢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來做咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍋裡放少許油 把洋蔥煎到金黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金黃色？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來依次加入馬鈴薯 胡蘿蔔 肉 再翻炒一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後加水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮一段時間之後 撇淨浮泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把咖哩塊煮化之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 再加上這些風味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加進去之後超好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米飯也做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米飯稍微有點焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍋巴好香！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩也做得好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全吃不出來巧克力味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃出來就不叫風味啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好多 可以添碗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放那麼多美乃滋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放的還算少呢 登山的時候需要卡路里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便放下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 日向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著心跳上升！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向好過分！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只管自己洗澡 都不幫忙收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵也去洗啊 好舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在別人家洗澡 總有些拘謹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒伸開手腳泡澡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 人間天堂 人間天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 小楓學姐這樣不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐 快穿衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉 壞習慣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜醬 不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來覺得挺寬敞 但四個人進來就顯得擠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你再往那邊點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山小屋還有比這更擠的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旺季簡直是大通鋪 人擠人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擠得跟早高峰的電車一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣也能睡著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都累壞了 睡得可香了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再做荷蘭美乃滋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用好多奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著就想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我也做做看 火腿蛋鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們玩單詞接龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只許說山名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等 剛才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.88,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日語中没有鼻音ん(n)開頭的單詞 所以說音讀「山(san)」結尾的就算輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尾山！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:07.78,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尾山 第一季中介紹過的山 位於東京郊外 感興趣的同學請觀看第一季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐山！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:12.44,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐山 位於青森縣下總半島中部的火山 海拔878公尺 以溫泉眾多聞名\N是一座與山嶽信仰和佛教信仰淵源深厚的靈山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉韋厄火山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時候也不早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情感熱線時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情感？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有四個女生喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從小葵說起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在喜歡誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又來這套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟米田君後來如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:29.20,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米田君 第一季故事中小葵幼年時的緋聞男友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼扯到小學的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先說說你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果非要說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的是山喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可可娜醬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜歡的人嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對夢馬君不能自拔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢馬君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:46.75,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢馬君 本故事的舞台琦玉縣飯能市的吉祥物（之一…）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉有點長 又毛茸茸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:10:35.18,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日語歌曲『岳人の歌』 詞曲作者不詳 是日本歌唱登山者的名曲之一

Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}星が降るあのコル グリセードで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}あの人は来るかしら 花をくわえて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}アルプスの恋唄 心ときめくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}懐かしの岳人 やさしかの君 やさしかの君

Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}踏著皚皚白雪 穿過滿天星空的圈谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}嘴裡銜著鮮花的他 會不會來尋覓我的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}阿爾卑斯的戀曲 讓人怦然心動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}回憶中的登山家 是溫柔的你 是溫柔的你…

Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向！要振作啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會丟下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 我吃得好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄啊 馬上就到山頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起當大眾情…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫家不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 日向好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵起得好早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由得就想起來 小時候我們一起看的日出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果從富士山看 一定會更美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起露營 真高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要到真正的山裡露營呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 不思議と どうしてかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:12.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミが笑うと 心の奥いつもキラリまたたく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's little step! 一歩ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's feel skip! 一緒にねっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気がつけば 夢中になってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:35.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「そういうコトあるよね」って言ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:41.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キュッと手と手つないだら 伝わる ぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:46.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこにでも行けちゃう気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:52.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tin-Ton-Tan 踏み出した瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:58.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界がパノラマみたいにひらけたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:03.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile こんな空の広さ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:09.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人きりじゃ きっと気づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:14.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 笑顔こだましてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:22.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸に広がる やさしい うれしい あたらしい予感たち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:27.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一歩一歩進んで行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 多麼不可思議 是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:12.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你微笑 心中就像繁星般閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's little step! 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's feel skip! 一起來呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來 已經沉浸其中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:35.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你對我說 「常有的事情！」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:41.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著緊握的雙手 傳來你的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:46.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿能走到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:52.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叮 咚 鐺 邁出一步的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:58.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界像全景照片一樣展現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:03.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 如此廣闊的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:09.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隻身一人 一定不會發現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:14.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 笑容在迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:22.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿內心的溫柔和喜悅 還有新的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:27.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步一步往前走吧！